{"word":"G4958 - συστέλλω - systéllō - soos-tel'-lo - Short","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συστέλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">systéllō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soos-tel'-lo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Short</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சுற்று, குறுகியதாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to draw together, contact"},{"paragraph":"2. to roll together, wrap up, wrap round with bandages, etc., to enshroud"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G4724 - στέλλω - stéllō - stel'-lo/4724\">G4724</a>; to <i>send</i> (<i>draw</i>) <i>together</i>, that is, <i>enwrap</i> (<i>enshroud</i> a corpse for burial), <i>contract</i> (an interval): - short, wind up.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1291/1291\">G1291</a>, <a href=\"#/G1293/1293\">G1293</a>, <a href=\"#/G1989/1989\">G1989</a>, <a href=\"#/G1992/1992\">G1992</a>, <a href=\"#/G2687/2687\">G2687</a>, <a href=\"#/G2689/2689\">G2689</a>, <a href=\"#/G4724/4724\">G4724</a>, <a href=\"#/G4958/4958\">G4958</a>, <a href=\"#/G5288/5288\">G5288</a>, <a href=\"#/G5289/5289\">G5289</a>"}]}